metadata.name: Status .tagged_with_none when given one tag returns the expected statuses

sql_query.sql: SELECT "statuses"."id" FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND (NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM statuses_tags forbidden WHERE forbidden.status_id = statuses.id AND forbidden.tag_id IN (1161))) ORDER BY "statuses"."id" ASC
